message: Where can I easily find rainbow pigeons? They're the only animal I'm missing in the compendium
They spawn pretty frequently along the path up mt lanayru. Another trick you can do is use ice arrows or ice weapons on normal chu jelly to turn it into white jelly
Hey thanks I found a bunch of them at hyrule ridge
Sidequest spoiler: If you do the sidequest with the sheikah ball in kakariko you fight a yiga with a windcleaver as part of the quest.
If you want speed boost potions, I think fleet lotus seeds are easier to get since you don't have to climb to find them. I think they're found in the zora region
10 upgrades or 3 full rings total
Maybe the dlc will add 3 more heart containers. I know they're adding at least 1 dungeon so there's hope
Then I think you'll just have to find one randomly. I seem to get attacked by yiga more often when traveling along main roads on foot
Yeah, I guess I could have

I think you can get another rarely from the amiibo
I think the only animals you can ride are deer, bears, and horses
